EPAL_X: Lock the sprite facing towards the positive X-axis
EPAL_Y: Lock the sprite facing towards the positive Y-axis
EPAL_Z: Lock the sprite facing towards the positive Z-axis
EPAL_NEGATIVE_X: Lock the sprite facing towards the negative X-axis
EPAL_NEGATIVE_Y: Lock the sprite facing towards the negative Y-axis
EPAL_NEGATIVE_Z: Lock the sprite facing towards the negative Z-axis
EPAL_ROTATE_X: Lock the sprite rotation on the X-axis
EPAL_ROTATE_Y: Lock the sprite rotation on the Y-axis
EPAL_ROTATE_Z: Lock the sprite rotation on the Z-axis
